Ext.data.JsonP['Determining_Your_Studio_Configuration']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Determining Your Studio Configuration</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083287\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Determining Your Studio Configuration</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083287_DeterminingYourStudioConfiguration-Contents\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Contents</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Determining_Your_Studio_Configuration-section-src-30083287_DeterminingYourStudioConfiguration-Overview\">Overview</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Determining_Your_Studio_Configuration-section-src-30083287_safe-id-RGV0ZXJtaW5pbmdZb3VyU3R1ZGlvQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbi1XaHlTZW5kdGhlQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbkxvZz8\">Why Send the Configuration Log?</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Determining_Your_Studio_Configuration-section-src-30083287_safe-id-RGV0ZXJtaW5pbmdZb3VyU3R1ZGlvQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbi1Ib3d0b0lnZXRhY2Nlc3N0b3RoZWNvbmZpZ3VyYXRpb25sb2c_\">How to I get access to the configuration log?</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083287_DeterminingYourStudioConfiguration-Overview\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Overview</span></h2>\n    <p>Occasionally, Studio developers will ask to see your configuration log. You can access it by following the directions below.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083287_safe-id-RGV0ZXJtaW5pbmdZb3VyU3R1ZGlvQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbi1XaHlTZW5kdGhlQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbkxvZz8\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Why Send the Configuration Log?</span></h2>\n    <p>When submitting a bug, the more information we can collect from the user initially will decrease or response and resolution time.  The configuration log helps us to know which plugins the users is running and has upgraded from.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083287_safe-id-RGV0ZXJtaW5pbmdZb3VyU3R1ZGlvQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbi1Ib3d0b0lnZXRhY2Nlc3N0b3RoZWNvbmZpZ3VyYXRpb25sb2c_\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>How to I get access to the configuration log?</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Go to <strong class=\" \">Help-&gt;About Studio</strong> (or <strong class=\" \">Studio -&gt; About Studio</strong> for Mac users)    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Installation Details</strong> button    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select the <strong class=\" \">Configuration</strong> tab.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">Copy to Clipboard</strong> button    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Paste your <strong class=\" \">clipboard copy</strong> into any text editor.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Save and attach the text file.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083287\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Determining Your Studio Configuration"});